document_data.Trivia:
* The [[red dragon]] [[Velcuthimmorhar]] was also known by the alias "Hephaestus" in reference to him.
* Within the Realms there existed a [[book]] titled ''[[Hephaestus, God of Blacksmiths]]''. One copy of this tome laid within [[Bard Keep]], a temple of [[Oghma]] that stood within [[the North]] near [[Silverymoon]].{{Cite dungeon/29/Ex Libris|38}}
* The deity was known to the [[firbolg]] [[Morten]] under his alias Vulcan. When Morten had a hot [[fire poker]] pressed against his face by the [[hill giant]] chieftain [[Noote]] in [[1366 DR]], he compared the pain filling his head to being hit by Vulcan's hammer.<ref>
